properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 5 at 12:21PM EST until January 5 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
rough waters.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST THIS EVENING... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
